  "meta": {
    "title": "Awesome Conformal Prediction [![Awesome](https://awesome.re/badge-flat.svg)](https://awesome.re) [![DOI](https://zenodo.org/badge/436989758.svg)](https://zenodo.org/badge/latestdoi/436989758)",
